graph TD
    User["Sales Rep"]
    Coordinator["Louna<br/>(Main Coordinator Agent)"]
    ZTCust[("Zapier Table:<br/>Quickbook Customers")]
    ZTProd[("Zapier Table:<br/>Quickbook Products")]
    Pricing["Pricing Agent"]
    Invoice["Invoice History Agent"]
    Logistics["Logistics Agent"]
    BQ[("BigQuery<br/>knoxx-foods-451311.TempTest")]

    User <-->|Chat| Coordinator

    Coordinator -->|Semantic search:<br/>resolve customer name → ID| ZTCust
    Coordinator -->|Semantic search:<br/>resolve product name → ID| ZTProd

    Coordinator -->|product_id, customer_id| Pricing
    Coordinator -->|customer_id, product_id| Invoice
    Coordinator -->|product_id, container_number| Logistics

    Pricing -->|Cost inputs, RSP,<br/>peer prices, margin check| BQ
    Invoice -->|Invoice line items,<br/>trends, volumes| BQ
    Logistics -->|Landed cost, charges,<br/>shipping agreements| BQ

    Pricing -->|Recommendation +<br/>internal flags| Coordinator
    Invoice -->|History summary| Coordinator
    Logistics -->|Cost breakdown +<br/>internal flags| Coordinator

    style Coordinator fill:#4A90D9,stroke:#2C5F8A,color:#fff
    style Pricing fill:#7B68EE,stroke:#5A4FCF,color:#fff
    style Invoice fill:#7B68EE,stroke:#5A4FCF,color:#fff
    style Logistics fill:#7B68EE,stroke:#5A4FCF,color:#fff
    style ZTCust fill:#FF8C00,stroke:#CC7000,color:#fff
    style ZTProd fill:#FF8C00,stroke:#CC7000,color:#fff
    style BQ fill:#34A853,stroke:#2D8E47,color:#fff
    style User fill:#555,stroke:#333,color:#fff
